  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Anticipatory Water, Sanitation and Hygiene (WASH) Actions to Prevent and Reduce Human Suffering, Through Provision of Clean Safe Water and Hygiene Promotion Services</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IOM is ensuring sustainable access to clean water and preventative hygiene services for Somali communities living in districts affected by COVID-19, locusts, and flooding. Activities include the rehabilitation and upgrading of existing boreholes and shallow wells, water treatment and provision of water treatment products, and hygiene promotion.</narrative>
  </description>
